casebody.data:
Miguel ARGUETA, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
BRISTOL NMB PARTNERS, Limited Partnership, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1933 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 14, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of certiorari, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
